        {
          "text": "Our college faculty is most supportive and friendly in nature.",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The overall strategy of our college is nice and helpful",
          "name": "beauty kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers and faculty are good and very good of nature",
          "name": "beauty kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the involvement of teachers in our studies",
          "name": "beauty kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "I am only first year and it's only been 2-3 weeks . If talk about area it's around 17 acers . There are 6-7 buildings in campus in which one is of btech , one 1 is of pharmacy , one is of management and 2 of hostels and 1 of diploma.",
          "name": "Aryan Nath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Classrooms Are Cleaned For The Daily Basis and there is disciplined mainted",
          "name": "Shivam Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Seminar:- in a month there are 3to 4 times seminar organised by professional",
          "name": "Kunal gangwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus environment:- it has fully green environment, cafe restaurant and all fun things",
          "name": "Kunal gangwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Circular Activity:- on every week there has organised sports, fest amd other things",
          "name": "Kunal gangwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel life there is every thing which you want to be in a hostel  it have a gym all games area provided 24×7 Electricity is provided",
          "name": "Harsh vardhan chaudhary",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Bad classrooms . There is no air circulation in classes we can't able to study because of heat and sweat",
          "name": "Aryan Nath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Bad management of area , I think they have enough space for a college but still they are not using it effectively the structure of buildings are so old many of area ruins",
          "name": "Aryan Nath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Exam will conduct in every month, you lost the fear of exam.",
